properties.Name: InventoryReservation
properties.Description:
A guaranteed allotment of the associated Product in regard to the Order.    

An inventory hold is placed on the quantity of Product at the warehouse to be sure that the Order can be fulfilled.

Columns.Name: InventoryReservationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Inventory Reservation.

Columns.Name: WarehouseId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Warehouse.

Columns.Name: ReservationProductQuantity
Columns.Description: The quantity of the Inventory Reservation.

Columns.Name: InventoryReservationDate
Columns.Description: The date of the Inventory Reservation.

Columns.Name: InventoryReservationNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Inventory Reservation.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: OrderId
Columns.Description: The unique number that identifies an Order.
